title._content: Geyser at a hot springs near Lakeview, circa 1940

description._content: Description/Notes: Geyser at Hoetars Hot Springs- Lakeview. The geese in the foreground are so well fed that they tend to stay around the hotel where they amuse guests. See the geyser in the rear of the photo. Lake County has the only two active geysers in Oregon.
